tags.description: The 2021-12-30 Marshall Fire burned the building & Supercharger station. Superchargers came back online 2022-04-30 but the building was damaged so much that they gutted it to the steel structure & rebuilt it. Reopened 2023-05-20 with an open house party.
tags.name: Tesla Service Colorado-Superior
tags.note: Tesla sales has a room in the NE corner of the building, but was told in person 2024-08-07 that this location is no longer a delivery center.
